  \/ M - M O D I F Y \/

SCREENEDIT specified lines

Format
 MODIFY <line no.>,<no. of lines>

Parameters
 <line #>  # of 1st line to edit. Must be specified.
 <# lines> # of lines to be edited. Optional - taken as 1 if not specified. ESC
           key will terminate editing before this number of lines has been
           edited, if required.

File position
 The file is left positioned after the last line edited.
